body.name: Qilmy Mardi Gras Cloth Napkins Set of 6, Reusable Washable Polyester Dinner Table Napkins for Family, Weddings, Parties, Home Decor, 20 x 20 Inch
features: 【Eco-friendly Cloth Napkins】 - Reduce paper waste by switching to our durable cloth napkins, it is made of premium satin polyester, soft feeling and silky touch, designed to avoid stains and wrinkles, hemmed edges and seamless construction give the napkin strength and durability, the dinner cloth napkins are oversized 20"x20" so you can use it better.

【Elegant Napkins for Any Meal】 - This reuseable cloth napkin set is a great decoration for your home or farmhouse for everyday use, can be used during meals for decorating kitchen table or dining room, pair it with additional tabletop collection to create a unique table decor that your friends and family will love.

【Multi-purpose Dinner Napkins】- Our excellent and luxury hotel quality napkins are best for use both in business or home settings; great as hotel napkins, wedding napkins, restaurant napkins, banquet table napkins, cocktail napkins and as party table napkins.
【Various Design Options】 - All dinner napkins are personalized with vivid color and non-fading, it available in a variety of design options, you're sure to find exactly what you're looking for.
【Easy to Care】- Machine washable, gentle cycle, tumble dry low, low iron if needed; if you have any questions can contact us at any time.
